Third-Party Dependencies

This project uses open-source components from the Rust ecosystem.
A complete list of all 446 third-party crate licenses is available in
THIRDPARTY_LICENSES.

Notable dependencies include but are not limited to:

  axum (MIT)               — HTTP framework
  tokio (MIT)              — Async runtime
  ratatui (MIT)            — Terminal UI
  wasmtime (Apache-2.0)   — WASM runtime
  sqlx (MIT OR Apache-2.0) — PostgreSQL driver
  crossterm (MIT)          — Terminal manipulation
  clap (MIT OR Apache-2.0) — CLI argument parser
  reqwest (MIT OR Apache-2.0) — HTTP client
  serde (MIT OR Apache-2.0) — Serialization framework
